content.rendered:
Directed by Gurmmeet Singh.

Written by Vivek Chaudhary. Vivek Chaudhary. Rajesh Chawla. Banga Gagan. Anand Kumar.

Cast Zayed Khan(Prithvi Khurana). Tina Desai(Megha). Anupam Kher(D. K. Thawani). Rannvijay Singh(Sam). Talia Bentson(Rashida). Yuri Suri(G. S. Chaddha). Shomendra Bose(Agyatshatru). Rinku(Angry Driver). Satish Murugesan(Petrol Pump Attendant (as Satish Murgesan)). Anay Verma(Begger). Gurjeet Singh Arora(Angry Sardarji (as Gurdeep Singh Arora)). Poonam(Laxmi). Vishal Bajaj(Man on Bike). Vipul Chaube(Man in Car at Red Light Signal). Sanjeev Chauhan(Police Inspector). Devinder Jain(New Client). Aditi Seshadri(Megha’s Colleague). Naman Mehra(Vick). Mahavir Singh(Chhole Kulche Vendor). Hardeep Singh(Prithvi’s Boss). Manik Batra(Mr. Shah). Aditya Tendulkar(Waiter)

Language Hindi.

Producers Akhilesh Jain. Devinder Jain. Baljinder Singh.

Production Medios Entertainment.
